到這份工作。幾千個川普支持者傳訊威脅我的人身安全，但我還是不會停止為『黑人的命也是命』發聲。」<br />\n<br />\n之後克蕾拉又上傳了以下的影片哭訴：「川普支持者們讓我丟了工作。我之前接到一堆死亡和暴力威脅，那都沒關係，但現在連我的未來都黑掉了。你們這些支持『大家的命都是命』的種族歧視份子和川普支持者，你們無法擊倒我。丟掉工作很糟糕，但種族歧視更糟糕，我不會停止用我的平台發聲。我很遺憾德勤公司看不清這點，你們竟然開除了會為這個世界帶來重大改變的人。」<br />\n<br />\n克蕾拉後來因為失業造成財務困難，<span class=\"red\">發起網路募款，最後募到了約1萬2000美元。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"幾撚醒 臨尾都拖鳩侵支持者落水黎spin"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"今年5月從哈佛大學畢業，主修為政治與心理學。"},{"pid":"7551f87dc916cb34242e31c50a174e97085dcdf7","tid":2370021,"uid":156144,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:52:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">你們竟然開除了會為這個世界帶來重大改變的人</span><br />\n<br />\n屌CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7869c653372ac0a87afe2f793f209e43484de141","tid":2370021,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cbb57f11d9c7bcfa882b93ae2d204363f74f10b","tid":2370021,"uid":14494,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:26:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">種族歧視更糟糕</span><br />\n比講BLM, 但唔比講All live matter就唔係歧視? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:52:12.000Z","msg":"black live better"},{"pid":"e1866b49a16f6a34965d28bd76a52b8a6f4c2987","tid":2370021,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aebb22f38a93f632cae85c1c5461ce08450ae065","tid":2370021,"uid":17504,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"5d2bdabb931b194c35fafd4bd724